# Insulin Glargine Lantus

## Overview

Long-acting basal insulin analog providing once-daily glucose control.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Glargine Lantus |

## Mechanism of Action

A21 glycine, B31-B32 glycine modifications cause isoelectric precipitation at pH 4 dissolving slowly at physiological pH.

